description._content: Original Collection: Extension and Experiment Station Communications Item Number: P120:3651 Item Description: Jess A. Hansen, Corvallis, of Hansen's Leghorn Farm, is shown presenting a prize cockerel to Marion county 4-H club member, Martha Harper Brooks. The cockrel was presented for the pen of best White Leghorn pullets at the 1948 State Fair. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more?
